<section id="second-section-about">

        <h2> About Me </h2>
        	<p> I'm 24 years old, I'm from São Paulo - Brazil but I've been living in Cork since November 2018. I have a bachelor's degree in Design and I've been working as a Graphic Designer in many different publicity agencies for the past 5 years. I decided to pursue the Computing Science course since I want to follow the UI and UX career. </p>

          <p> As well as my vocation, Design is also one of my passions and today I'm proud to say that I chose this path for my life. Also, if anyone wants to see some of my work you can check <a href= "https://gustavoselemem.myportfolio.com/" target="_blank"> my portfolio </a></p>

</section>


<section id="third-section-about">

          <p> I love reading, playing video-games and any nerd stuff. One of my favourite books is Les Misérables by Victor Hugo which I actually have a tattoo of it! Music is also something that is present in every day of my life; I can't even imagine working without Spotify </p>

</section>


